    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's the thing, a journey usually implies you're looking for something new. i'm not. i feel like i've looked at everything there is to look at. every destination i hit just confirms that the world is a finished thing for me. it's like i've reached the edge of the map and there's just... nothing else on the other side. it feels more like a conclusion than a pause.",
